on(\\\"Property '${propertyName}' must contain absolute paths. Got: ${propertyValue}\\\")\\n        }\\n        if (!directory.isDirectory()) {\\n            throw new GradleException(\\\"Property '${propertyName}' must contain existing directories. Missing: ${directory.absolutePath}\\\")\\n        }\\n        return directory\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nString requiredAbsolutePathProperty(String propertyName) {\\n    String propertyValue = requiredGradleProperty(propertyName)\\n    if (!new File(propertyValue).isAbsolute()) {\\n        throw new GradleException(\\\"Property '${propertyName}' must contain an absolute path. Got: ${propertyValue}\\\")\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_61\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc 'rg -n \\\"extractLibraryTestParams\\\" -S tests/tck-build-logic/src/main tests/tck-build-logic/src/test'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_61\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc 'rg -n \\\"extractLibraryTestParams\\\" -S tests/tck-build-logic/src/main tests/tck-build-logic/src/test'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org.graalvm.internal.tck-harness.gradle:788:// gradle extractLibraryTestParams -Pcoordinates=<group:artifact[:version]>\\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org.graalvm.internal.tck-harness.gradle:789:tasks.register(\\\"extractLibraryTestParams\\\", DefaultTask) { task ->\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_62\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '780,840p' tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org.graalvm.internal.tck-harness.gradle\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_62\",\"type\":\"command_executi