{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_42","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2`.\n\nPreserved work is available here:\nhttps://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2653-library-new-request-org.apache.poi-poi-ooxml-4.1.2-8a9b1e8f\n\nThe most likely failing stage was test generation / handoff, not final library validation. In `logs/org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2/native-test-verify/cycle-2-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-11T13-41-30-860315Z.log`, native verification still runs the scaffold test `org_apache_poi.poi_ooxml.Poi_ooxmlTest > test()` and prints `This is just a placeholder, implement your test`, which means a placeholder test survived into the generation flow. Later validation looks green: `logs/org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-11T13-43-22-690564Z.log` and `logs/org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-11T13-44-07-754363Z.log` both show only `ObjectFactoryTest` and `SignatureConfigTest` passing, and `stats/org.apache.poi/poi-ooxml/4.1.2/execution-metrics.json` reports `status: success` with dynamic-access coverage `4/4 (100.00%)`. The later `logs/org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2/local-ci-fixup/run-consecutive-tests-2026-05-11T13-47-49-034059Z.log` appears unrelated noise because it is failing on `com.typesafe.akka:akka-serialization-jackson_3:2.6.21`, not on `poi-ooxml`.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `logs/org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2/native-test-verify/cycle-2-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-11T13-41-30-860315Z.log`\n- `logs/org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-11T13-43-22-690564Z.log`\n- `logs/org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-11T13-44-07-754363Z.log`\n- `stats/org.apache.poi/poi-ooxml/4.1.2/execution-metrics.json`\n\nNext steps:\n1. Review the preserved branch and confirm the final test set is the intended non-scaffold pair (`ObjectFactoryTest` and `SignatureConfigTest`) and that `Poi_ooxmlTest.java` is removed.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2` from the preserved branch to verify the final tree rather than the earlier placeholder-bearing snapshot.\n3. If that stays green, prepare the manual PR/update from the preserved branch; otherwise adjust/regenerate the tests so the scaffold placeholder never reaches native verification."}}
